    "shell": "default",
    "meta": {},
    "html": "<h2>Masters in Computer Science</h2>\n<p>The Masters page presents the degree as a two-year thesis-based programme intended to train students to evaluate and conduct world-class research.</p>\n<h3>Entry guidance from source</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Honours-level background in Computer Science (or approved equivalent)</li>\n<li>Supervisor agreement is essential before applying</li>\n<li>Applicants are encouraged to review research areas and publications before approaching supervisors</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Source: <a href=\"https://cs.sun.ac.za/teaching/masters/\">https://cs.sun.ac.za/teaching/masters/</a></p>\n",
